New /market-snapshot route with internal toggle (Heatmap | Movers). Both
sub-tabs draw from the same /api/market/quotes endpoint with different
visual treatment, so two separate sidebar entries was redundant.

Implementation:
- /market-snapshot/page.tsx tab-bar component with URL state (?tab=heatmap|movers)
- Dynamic-imports the existing /heatmap and /movers page components
  (only the active tab mounts, so the hidden tab does not run its queries)
- Original /heatmap and /movers routes kept alive for deeplink compatibility

Sidebar: 'Heatmap' + 'Movers' replaced by single 'Market Snap' entry
(reduces nav 15 -> 14 entries; combined with 0089's macro-maps + portfolios
removal, sidebar has gone 16 -> 14 in two patches).
